path.aria-label: List two diﬀerences between HL7v2 and FHIR:
xplanation: FHIR is the new standard developed by HL7.
List two diﬀerences between HL7v2 and FHIR:
HL7v2 uses a non-standard line format, where as FHIR uses XML or JSON
FHIR speciﬁes various resources that can be queried, where as HL7v2 has a number of ﬁxed ﬁelds
that are either ﬁlled in or not
